api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://political-bias-database.p.rapidapi.com/"

        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: fetch all allsides.com data
api_list.description: get request that returns entire allsides.com database as a json.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://political-bias-database.p.rapidapi.com/ASdata"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "political-bias-database.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
